{"tid":1624330,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"向外國人宣傳︰香港有政治清算，一旦反蒙面，香港人無法匿名發聲，開樣就清算","createTime":"2019-10-05T03:34:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T14:31:25.000Z","uid":54684,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"173d3439e23a357f4c43007c206aaf2e737ba24e","tid":1624330,"uid":54684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T03:34:36.000Z","msg":"呢個point先係最大問題，好多外國人未明白，<br />\n香港同外國唔同<br />\n香港有political censorship，<br />\n有政治打壓有秋後算帳<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>加拿大，美國，英國無政治清算，<br />\n開名開樣遊行無問題<br />\n無論你咩職業，身份，都可以自由發聲，無人可以因為咁制裁你，否則後果嚴重<br />\n總統畀國會劾，人權組織嚴重反彈，工會組織百萬人上街<br />\n</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">但係香港，係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">有</span>政治清算，<br />\n香港僱主會因為你對政府/大陸不滿，就解僱你，<br />\n梁振英會將你個名交畀大陸暗算<br />\n返工放工會畀藍絲打<br />\n大陸會向各階層施壓，傷害你，恐嚇你，削減你人身自由<br />\n有左反蒙面法，公務員，醫生護士，專業人士無法匿名發聲，<br />\n一開樣，現場無犯法，但事後就清算<br />\n反蒙面法係用來對付 和平，匿名既遊行示威人士，<br />\n要去expose佢地，欺負佢地，傷害佢地<br />\n呢個先係個point<br />\n</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n請認清楚個difference!<br />\n暴動既人如果被捉，本身暴動坐5~10年，依家蒙埋面 +1年，分別有限<br />\n和平合法示威既人，本身完全無罪，依家立即清算，解僱，名單交上大陸跟進<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">反蒙面法唔係用來對付&quot;violent rioters&quot;<br />\n反蒙面法係用來對付&quot;peaceful protesters who have to support the cause anonymously&quot;</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n文宣組，twitter組，reddit組，<br />\n要講清楚呢個point<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a457ce8687b299376dd2b6bb4799afc30a7cea6","tid":1624330,"uid":54684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T03:35:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fecfac2259740874349b629241f160c3853888f","tid":1624330,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T03:38:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d0fa9a57a196ac0a7140454c3317a54378524c3e","tid":1624330,"uid":54684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T03:40:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aabd9eca0c3ecadd1af8e642333b7b25a0cd2423","tid":1624330,"uid":167289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T03:44:03.000Z","msg":"推<div style=\"text-align: right;\"></div>"},{"pid":"d6fc1d74c7b400d7482d345a653d30d5b1558690","tid":1624330,"uid":284480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T04:03:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c15c76fca8ac17eaf5c2ed5d5c075f5597e8494a","tid":1624330,"uid":54684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T04:32:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"283520c8f60a7cbeded9a575473963662b83ba72","tid":1624330,"uid":54684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T04:50:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec65b62e63171d54e2295b59a0e0f3ff0b4c1f29","tid":1624330,"uid":279497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T04:53:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"73c513d26e91d9321800081d73fe8d93f84f9d7b","tid":1624330,"uid":54684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T09:49:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"679659d6d686bedbdabf0e81c6bf986b0b71cd84","tid":1624330,"uid":288360,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T10:14:25.000Z","msg":"For everyone who still doesn't understand why anti-masking laws are so dangerous:<br />\nIf peaceful citizens who wish to express themselves don't cover up, they know 100% that